    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__1508.
_:b0__1508 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2099-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2001-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/1003> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "105dc691-f823-4b65-9a76-f753b8160097";
