<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a7531bffefefcae22caeeda20854c8d4>.
<#a7531bffefefcae22caeeda20854c8d4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U17447>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-07T06:31:58.949Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
