<#18d6cddebc7642c6bfc2651dd75d4e52> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/n0cb-4f19> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "social förändring"@sv, "social change"@en, "sociala rörelser"@sv, "social movements"@en, "mammaaktivism"@sv, "mothering activism"@en, "ENVIRONMENT"@en, "MILJÖ"@sv, "ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGES"@en, "MILJÖFÖRÄNDRINGAR"@sv, "WELL-BEING (SOCIETY)"@en, "VÄLBEFINNANDE (SOCIALT)"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__24088.
_:b0__24088 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/8871b171a1812ec43597e9c47aff9118>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/n0cb-4f19> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021004896>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Denna datafil innehåller information om rörelser i global skala, som identifierats som huvudsakligen sammansatta av mödrar, fäder och andra som har nära kopplingar till ungdomar och barn, på uppdrag av vilka de söker och kräver förändring.\n\nUppgifterna som sammanfattas i denna fil handlar om grupper, rörelser och organisationer som i stor utsträckning består av mammor som i den rollen ägnar sig åt aktivism och relaterade aktiviteter i det offentliga rummet."@sv, "This datafile contains information about movements at a global scale, that were identified as being composed mainly by mothers, fathers and others who have close connections with youth and children, on behalf of whom they seek and demand change.\n\nThe data summarized in this file is about groups, movements and organizations made up in large extent of mothers who in that role engage in activism and related activities in the public sphere."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/8469e5c203fa5e320ea4b03458c1c7b2>, <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/7753cccac0952c05a71b47ed9117bfc7>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/n0cb-4f19#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2023-08-16T08:11:39.647798Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/n0cb-4f19>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2023-08-16T08:11:39.647798Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Inventering av Mothering and Fathering-aktivism för mer hållbara livsmiljöer"@sv, "Inventory of Mothering and Fathering Activism for More Sustainable Living Environments"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__84691.
_:b0__84691 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2023-04"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2023-03"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/n0cb-4f19> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
